It includes £1billion for the next phase of electrification between Manchester and York.  Transport Secretary Grant Shapps said: “This is the single biggest investment any government has made in the railways. It’s right up there and probably beyond what the Victorians were doing.” Transpennine Route Upgrades will deliver two more passenger trains an hour and slash journey times. The cash also sets the foundations for Northern Powerhouse Rail.  Transpennine Route Upgrades will deliver two more passenger trains an hour and slash journey times. The cash also sets the foundations for Northern Powerhouse Rail. 